'''相機陷阱'''指使用[[動作傳感器|動作傳感器]]、[[紅外探測器|紅外探測器]]或其他光束作為觸發機關的遙控[[相機|相機]]。它常被用來拍攝攝影師不容易直接拍得的畫面，多運用在生態研究領域，例如監督狩獵、觀察野生動物、尋找稀有物種等。<ref name="swann10">Swann, D. E., Kawanishi, K., Palmer, J. (2010) [http://books.google.com/books?id=onO2967GdPwC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA27#v=onepage&q&f=false ''Evaluating Types and Features of Camera Traps in Ecological Studies: A Guide for Researchers''] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=onO2967GdPwC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA27#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20170412142729 }}. In: O'Connell, A. F., Nichols, J. D., Karanth, U. K. (Eds.) 2010. ''Camera Traps in Animal Ecology: Methods and Analyses''. Springer, Tokyo, Dordrecht, London, Heidelberg, New York. ISBN 4-431-99494-7. Pages 27–43.</ref>

這種[[遙控相機|遙控相機]]的質量在近些年不斷得到提高，在野外觀察中也愈來愈流行。<ref name=CT1>{{cite web |title=WWF - Camera Traps - More on Camera Traps |url=http://www.worldwildlife.org/species/camera-traps/moreoncameratraps.html |work=World Wildlife Fund - Wildlife Conservation, Endangered Species Conservation |publisher=World Wildlife Fund |accessdate=4 October 2011 |archive-date=2012-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120512035105/http://www.worldwildlife.org/species/camera-traps/moreoncameratraps.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=CT2>{{cite web|title=Camera Traps for Researchers, Camera Trap Reviews and Tests.|url=http://www.trailcampro.com/cameratrapsforresearchers.aspx|work=Trail Cameras, Game Cameras Tests and Unbiased Reviews of Camera Traps|accessdate=4 October 2011|archive-date=2011-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008213912/http://www.trailcampro.com/cameratrapsforresearchers.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==應用==

相機陷阱的一大優點是它可以捕捉到更加精細的鏡頭，比起單純的人類觀察來說，它拍攝的影像還可以反復觀看。<ref name="swann10"/> 此外，相機陷阱可以持續、靜音運行，也很少會打擾到野生動物。<ref name=Cronin>{{cite journal|year=2010 |author=Cronin, S. |title=Camera trap talk |url=http://www.lps.org.au/camera%20traps.pdf |publisher=Photographic Society, April 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303225033/http://www.lps.org.au/camera%20traps.pdf |archivedate=2012-03-03 }}</ref> 不過因為有些動物嗅覺、聽覺極為敏銳，還是可以發現相機陷阱的蹤跡的。<ref name="swann10"/>

因為記載數據很精確，相機陷阱還可以用來計算一個地區的動物數量，這比單純靠人力來數要方便而實惠<ref name="TM"/>得多。此外還可以用來探測、尋找新的或珍稀物種。<ref name=CMT4>{{cite web|title=A-Z Animal Index|url=http://siwild.si.edu/index.cfm?species=155|work=Smithsonian Wild|publisher=Smithsonian|accessdate=29 November 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304032319/http://siwild.si.edu/index.cfm?species=155|dead-url=no}}</ref>
 
相機陷阱也可用來探測動物的行為和行動模式。<ref name=CT8>{{cite journal |author=Blake, J. G., Guerra, J., Mosquera, D., Torres, R., Loiselle, B. A., Romo, D. |title=Use of Mineral Licks by White-Bellied Spider Monkeys (Ateles belzebuth) and Red Howler Monkeys (Alouatta seniculus) in Eastern Ecuador |year=2010 |publisher=Internal Journal of Primatology |issue=31 |pages=471–483 |url=http://www.usfq.edu.ec/Tiputini/Research/Documents/Publicaciones/Blake%20John/fulltext%20%286%29.pdf |access-date=2013-08-30 |archive-date=2019-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190727234018/http://www.usfq.edu.ec/Tiputini/Research/Documents/Publicaciones/Blake%2520John/fulltext%2520(6).pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

